    "Furthermore, generated views should support interaction, allowing for more immersive user analysis.",
    "(C2) R3 Automatic insight generation: To reduce development costs, the system should efficiently complete code-based data analyses for given tasks, providing visualizations and suggesting findings to facilitate hypothesis forming and validation.",
